---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import person02 from "../assets/person02.png";
import lead_check_sp from "../assets/lead_check_sp.png";
---

<!-- こんな悩み -->
<div class="bg-white text-xl py-5">
	<div
		class="container bg-white rounded-3xl px-5 py-4 border-4 border-black drop-shadow-md [text-shadow:_0_1px_0_rgb(0_0_0_/_20%)] font-bold"
	>
		役員報酬(全額損金)を<br />
		<span class="underline">決算前に</span>増額できました。
	</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white text-xs py-5 px-1">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg">
		<div class="flex h-24 justify-center mb-5">
			<span class="left-up-line"></span><span
				class="flex items-center px-5 font-bold"
				><span class="text-3xl">革新的</span>な<span class="text-3xl">決済対策</span
				>がここにあります。</span
			><span class="right-up-line"></span>
		</div>
		<div
			class="relative bg-[#EFD4CE] rounded-3xl py-4 border-4 border-dashed border-black drop-shadow-md [text-shadow:_0_1px_0_rgb(0_0_0_/_20%)] font-bold flex flex-col pt-10"
		>
			<div class="ml-16">ある会社敬愛者の独り言...</div>
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex items-center flex-1 justify-center flex-col">
					<div
						class="bg-white rounded-3xl py-8 w-[300px] text-center shadow-xl"
					>
						今年は大幅に利益が上がった。<br
						/>役員報酬をもっと増やして<br />おくべきだった …。
					</div>
					<!-- <Image src={person02} alt="あるけ会社敬愛者" width=60 class="" /> -->
				</div>
				<div
					class="flex flex-col flex-1 justify-center items-center gap-5"
				>
					<div
						class="bg-white rounded-3xl py-8 w-[300px] text-center shadow-xl"
					>
						結局、交際費や消耗品費で<br
						/>経費を増やして利益を減らし<br />節税するしかないのか
						…。
					</div>
					<div
						class="bg-white rounded-3xl py-8 w-[300px] text-center shadow-xl"
					>
						決算月に高額の<br />役員報酬増額(損金)を<br
						/>したいが不可能だ …。
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<Image
				src={person02}
				alt=""
				width="120"
				class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="triangle ml-20 mb-80"></div>

<style>
	.right-up-line {
		width: 2px;
		background: #d66361;
		transform: rotate(35deg);
	}
	.left-up-line {
		width: 2px;
		background: #d66361;
		transform: rotate(140deg);
	}
	/* .sankaku {
		background-color: #008F8F;
		width: 25px;
		height: 20px;
		clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 50% 100%);
	} */
	
.triangle,
.triangle::before,
.triangle::after{
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  background: #ffbf7f;
}

.triangle::before,
.triangle::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
}

.triangle {
  position: relative;
  border-top-left-radius: 30%;
  transform: rotate(90deg) skewY(30deg) scaleX(.86666);
}

.triangle::before {
  border-top-right-radius: 30%;
  transform: skewX(-45deg) translateX(50%);
}

.triangle::after {
  border-bottom-left-radius: 30%;
  transform: skewY(-45deg) translateY(50%);
}

</style>